User
    ident Text
    email Email
    password Text Maybe
    verkey VerKey Maybe
    UniqueUser ident
    UniqueEmail email
    deriving Typeable
    deriving Show
Comment json -- Adding "json" causes ToJSON and FromJSON instances to be derived.
    message Text
    userId UserId Maybe
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show

Article json
    title Text
    content Text
    userId UserId
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show

Company json
    title Text
    userId UserId
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show

Event
    title Text
    content Text
    userId UserId
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show

GroupMembership
    state GroupMembershipState
    created UTCTime default=CURRENT_TIME
    userId UserId
    companyId CompanyId
    UniqueMembershipUserId userId companyId
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show

AccessToken
    created UTCTime default=CURRENT_TIME
    userId UserId
    token Text
    UniqueUserId userId
    UniqueToken token
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show


